  m_text: In May 1998, two cannons were lifted from the wreck. The lifting was carried
    out by EOD divers from the Gulf of Finland.  The cannon lifted from the location
    of this board is a 24- pounder naval cannon. The second shoulder pin of the cannon
    is marked EB which refers to the Swedish Ehrendahl foundry. The current weight
    of the cannon is 1800 kg. The original weight of the cannon was 2091 kg.
